  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">J.W. Sharp</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1867-07-22">July 22, 1867</date>
      <name type="place">Bath C.H. Va.</name>
     </dateline>
     <salute>Dear Sir,</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I have diligently searched the records of my Office to find the order of Court, directing the
     "Overseers of the Poor" to bind Mary Gordon to Stewart C Slaven. and can find no such order, I
     searched the records for the past twenty years Neither do I find any "articles of Indenture"
     between such parties, filed in my Office. I think there must be some mistake in regard to her
     being bound by the Overseers of the Poor of this County. </p>

    <closer>
     <salute>Very Respectfully</salute>
     <signed>C. R McDonnald Clk </signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
